    <div id="home" class="content">
        <h2>Why did I decide to open up a cardshop?</h2>
        <p>From a young age I started collecting cards. There was something about getting a pack of cards and opening up the pack to find mystery cards. These cards ranged from sports cards to Pokemon cards. I would take all the cool cards I collected from packs and show them off at school or trade with other kids who had cards. From that day I was inspired and dreamed of owning a cardshop of my own. About as year ago I opeend up my very own card shop and started living my dream. I have been very happy and wouldn't change a thing! I hope you find what you want on my website! Thanks for the support! </p>
		<h2>What's all on this website?</h2>
		<p>I have created a pokedex so anyone can see all the pokemon and what type they are, what they are weak to, and more. I am working on creating a pokedev with the first generation pokemon and have only done the first nine but will finish the rest soon. I am also starting to sell some of my big pulls and cards I have been collecting since I was a kid. I think it's time someone else enjoys these cards I've been holding on to for a long time. Keep an eye out for giveaways as I will be giving out free stuff on my social media. You can find my social media links on the giveaway page.</p>
	</div>		

